# Python recursive ignores
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/*$py.class
**/build*/
**/dist*/
**/_internal*/
**/Portable*/
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.mypy_cache/

# Binary Distribution folders (Recursive)
**/ChainFlow_V21_Suite/
**/_ARCHIVE*/
**/_legacy_experiments*/

